import React from 'react'
import Headx from '../components/Headx'
import { Container, Row, Col, Jumbotron, Card, CardImg, CardText, CardBody,
    CardTitle, CardSubtitle} from 'reactstrap'
function contact() {
    return (
        <Headx title={'About Us'}>
            <Container style={{background:'#fff'}}>
                <Row>
                    <Col md="12" style={{marginTop:'60px'}}>
                        <Card style={{marginTop:'20px', marginBottom:'20px'}}>
                                <CardImg top width="50%" height="400px" src="../static/image/contact/contact.jpg" alt="contact" />
                                <CardBody>
                                    <CardTitle className="text-center">Contact US</CardTitle>
                                </CardBody>
                        </Card>  
                    </Col>
                </Row>
            </Container>
        </Headx>
    )
}

export default contact
